item.title: CVE-2023-5559|2024-08-02T07:59:44.808Z -- unknown -- 10web%20booster
item.description: The 10Web Booster WordPress plugin before 2.24.18 does not validate the option name given to some AJAX actions, allowing unauthenticated users to delete arbitrary options from the database, leading to denial of service.
